      • PROP_KEY_ANALYSIS_DEPTH

        public static final AppConfigPropertiesKeys PROP_KEY_ANALYSIS_DEPTH
        Key for the index analysis depth, i.e. the opening moves depth: "luchess.configuration.analysis.depth". Moves will be indexed only up to the analysis depth, which means that fast search and continuations will be available only up to that threshold. The higher the analysis depth, the bigger the index, the slower the indexing, the faster the search. Searches beyond the analysis depth remain possible, but will be slower and will not offer continuations. The default analysis depth should be set to the average length of common chess openings.
        See Also:
        Continuation
